    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.3
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "今日の「おはテレ」のゲストは……",
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host001.m4a",
      "text": "大人気アイドル、TRINITYAiLEです！",
      "startTime": 3.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "あの『ぷりてぃー★エンジェル』の舞台に出演が",
      "startTime": 6.8333329678,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host002.m4a",
      "text": "決まって大注目の三人に、お話を聞いてみましょう",
      "startTime": 9.1666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-smr001.m4a",
      "text": "よろしくお願いします～",
      "startTime": 14.0333336354,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 16.3131522418
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "鈴村さんは日本を代表する名優、鈴村久美子さんの",
      "startTime": 16.3131522418,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host003.m4a",
      "text": "娘さんです。演技のお仕事は、今回が初めてですか？",
      "startTime": 21.0666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "最近は全くですが、実はすでに生まれてすぐお母さんと",
      "startTime": 25.8131526233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu002.m4a",
      "text": "ドラマで共演してて。役者デビューは早いんですよね",
      "startTime": 30.7131526233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 35.57981929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "小さい頃からお母さんの演技をそばで見て",
      "startTime": 35.57981929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu003.m4a",
      "text": "育ってきましたから、少しは演技に自信あります",
      "startTime": 38.8387169783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 43.1131526233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "長く愛されてる原作ですから、うちらが演じるのを",
      "startTime": 43.1131526233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu004.m4a",
      "text": "ファンのみなさんは、不安に思われるでしょうけど――",
      "startTime": 47.2464859566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 50.77981929
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "役者として、そして作品のいちファンとして……",
      "startTime": 50.77981929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu005.m4a",
      "text": "絶対いい舞台にしてみせます。観に来て損はさせません",
      "startTime": 55.57981929,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 60.5131526233
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "さすが優ね。アイドルのキャスティングに",
      "startTime": 60.5131526233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-rui002.m4a",
      "text": "否定的な意見があることを分かったうえで……",
      "startTime": 63.8464859566,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "うん。反感を持たれないように、言葉を選んで",
      "startTime": 67.1131526233,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-smr002.m4a",
      "text": "うまく宣伝してくれてる。頼りになるなぁ",
      "startTime": 71.0944027068,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 75.2038784267
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それは期待出来ますね。今回の舞台、演出家は厳しい",
      "startTime": 75.2038784267,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host004.m4a",
      "text": "ことで有名なあの蟻田さんですが……大丈夫ですか？",
      "startTime": 79.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ふふ……どれだけ厳しいしごきが待ってるのか",
      "startTime": 85.3038830043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu006.m4a",
      "text": "楽しみにしとります",
      "startTime": 89.6372163376,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 91.570549671
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（子役時代、先輩の役者さんからも相当厳しいって）",
      "startTime": 91.570549671,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "smr",
      "speakerName": "奥山すみれ",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sumire.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-smr003.m4a",
      "text": "（聞いた気が……この放送を観てたら、大変なことに……）",
      "startTime": 95.7333385945,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 101.300050823
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "だって、うちらがしごかれればしごかれるほど……",
      "startTime": 101.300050823,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu007.m4a",
      "text": "……みなさんに、ええ舞台をお届け出来るやん？",
      "startTime": 105.3667174896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.5667174896
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "一同",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host005.m4a",
      "text": "（さっすが～！！）",
      "startTime": 108.5667174896,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 112.2530450345
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それでは、恒例のゲストによるジェスチャーゲームの",
      "startTime": 113.2530445259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host006.m4a",
      "text": "お時間です！　ジェスチャー役は誰に……",
      "startTime": 116.9940438643,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 120.5863865059
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "はいはい、うちがジェスチャー役をやらせてもらいます",
      "startTime": 120.5863865059,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu008.m4a",
      "text": "舞台に先駆けて、うちの演技を初公開しちゃいます",
      "startTime": 124.9473206045,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 129.4530531725
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ありがとう、優。ジェスチャー役を買って出てくれて",
      "startTime": 129.4530531725,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-rui004.m4a",
      "text": "演技が未熟な私のため……よね",
      "startTime": 133.6333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 136.6530552071
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "ええんよ。うちも、これまで数えきれないくらい",
      "startTime": 136.6530552071,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "yu",
      "speakerName": "鈴村優",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-yu.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-yu009.m4a",
      "text": "瑠依ちゃんに一杯助けてもらってきたんやから",
      "startTime": 140.586389049,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 143.8197218737
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "unknown",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "それではゲームスタートです！　鈴村さんが演じる",
      "startTime": 143.8197218737,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "host",
      "speakerName": "司会者",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-host007.m4a",
      "text": "動物を天動さんと奥山さんが当てて下さい！",
      "startTime": 147.4333353679,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 151.753047069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "（優がジェスチャーを開始したわね……ふむふむ）",
      "startTime": 151.753047069,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02/sud_vo_adv_event_2409_01_02-rui005.m4a",
      "text": "（手と足を全部地面につけて歩いてる……四本足？）",
      "startTime": 156.6587716752,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_talkstudio-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "talkstudio-00-noon",
      "startTime": 162.553047069
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
